      "id": "modality-guideline-hands-occupied",
      "content": "When the user activity sensor reports the state \"hands-occupied\", prefer audio-first guidance. Provide spoken prompts and minimize the need for direct touch input. When the sensor reports \"hands-free\", present tactile controls such as buttons or toggles for the light switch.",
