      "id": "user-preference-primary-color",
      "content": "The primary household preference for interface accents is the color \"#1F6FEB\" (a vivid cobalt). Whenever possible, set the UI theme primary color to this value so buttons, toggles, and other interactive highlights align with the user preference. Ensure sufficient contrast by using light text on dark backgrounds.",
